name: pyls-flake8
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyls-flake8" %}
{% set version = "0.4.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/pyls-flake8-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 630cec96e494c0f3bffa381451d71a05f46b4f4e6d9b897ad6377e81cc4f8f70

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - flake8 >=3.6.0
    - python >=3.6
    - python-lsp-server

test:
  imports:
    - pyls_flake8
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/emanspeaks/pyls-flake8
  summary: A Flake8 plugin for the Python Language Server
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - asford
